* Build the Docker container running **./build.sh** and following the instructions on screen
* Run the container with **./run.sh**
* In download-cnaf-FS3.py choose the files you want to download (start_file, end_file) and the length of the time interval (deltat)
* Run the python script with **python3 download-cnaf-FS3.py**
* After the file has run you can check the downloaded files in /root/glitches, together with the number of the channels and the ones which failed to download for each glitch.
